nodes.body: I'm a bit worried about new `import`s in basic files, otherwise LGTM.

Importing `aesop` seems fair game to me. Importing `Data.Pi.Algebra` I want to say is not my problem since it's still a mess to know what belongs in `Data.Pi.Algebra` vs `Algebra.Group.Pi`, and probably these files should be reorganised (which is out of scope for this PR).

Pull request successfully merged into master.
